Story_Texts.SourceString: It's the very dangerous land of Burny Volcano!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: It's the very dangerous land of Burny Volcano!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Don't worry team, I brought a supply of aloe vera!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Why did we rescue him again?
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Why did we rescue him again?

Story_Texts.SourceString: I believe it was a plot device to move the story forward…
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: I believe it was a plot device to move the story forward…

Story_Texts.SourceString: Yaijan was the keeper of the Crystal Forge and possessor of a majestic mustache.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Yaijan was the keeper of the Crystal Forge and possessor of a majestic mustache.

Story_Texts.SourceString: It seems that Zerath's corruption and dubious facial hair have gotten to him!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: It seems that Zerath's corruption and dubious facial hair have gotten to him!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Come on guys, I think it's time Yaijan gets a shave!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Come on guys, I think it's time Yaijan gets a shave!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Our heroes venture forth, aloe vera and shaving cream in hand.
